  .guide.wide.timeline
    .content
      h2 Previous iterations
      ul.visual.flag-list
        li.flag-item
          span.flag: img.border(src='/assets/images/flag-louisiana-1861.svg', alt='thirteen stripes of alternating blue, white, red, white; a canton of red with a gold star')
          h4 1861
          p Flag raised during the weeks between seceding from the United States and joining the Confederacy.
        li.flag-item
          span.flag: img(src='/assets/images/flag-louisiana-pelican-1861.jpg', alt='a field of blue with an early rendering of thee pelican emblem')
          h4 1861
          p Flag raised at a similar time, establishing the pelican iconography. It was flown simultaneously with the flags of the Confederacy.
        li.flag-item
          span.flag: img(src='/assets/images/flag-louisiana-1912-2006.jpg', alt='')
          h4 1912-2006
          p A variation of the pelican flag with the red droplets of blood missing.
        li.flag-item
          span.flag: img(src='/assets/images/flag-louisiana.svg', alt='current Louisiana flag')
          h4 2010-Present
          p The current flag, following the standards defined by Louisiana statute.

